TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seem high. Me give 200 only.
Here be 250 gold. Now me own you, Linu.
Text: 여기 250 금화. 이제 넌 내 거야, 리누.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seems a little expensive. I'll give you 200.
225? Deal.
I could use a good healer. Here's your 250 gold. Welcome aboard, Linu.
Text: 좋은 치유사가 필요했어. 250 금화 여기 있어. 환영해, 리누.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seem high. Me give 150 only.
Here be 200 gold. Now me own you, Linu.
Text: 여기 200 금화. 이제 넌 내 거야, 리누.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seems a little expensive. I'll give you 150.
175? Deal.
I could use a good healer. Here's your 200 gold. Welcome aboard, Linu.
Text: 좋은 치유사가 필요해. 여기 금화 200개 있어. 환영해, 리누.

TextEng: Me go now.
Me not got that much gold for spend on you.
Text: 나 너한테 쓸 그만큼 금화 없어.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seem high. Me give 100 only.
Here be you 150 gold. Now me own you, Linu.
Text: 여기 너의 금화 150개. 이제 나 너 소유해, 리누.

TextEng: I'll be going now.
I don't have that kind of gold to spend on a henchman.
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> That seems a little expensive. I'll give you 100.
125? Deal.
I need a good healer. Here's your 150 gold. Welcome aboard, Linu.
Text: 좋은 치유사가 필요해. 여기 금화 150개 있어. 환영해, 리누.

TextEng: No.
Yes.
No, not now.
Yes.
Me be the greaterest, er... bestest! Yeah, me be the bestest!
Text: 나는 최고의, 어... 가장 좋은! 그래, 나는 가장 좋은!

TextEng: Why they sing? Me just do duty.
Text: 왜 노래해? 나는 그냥 임무 한 거야.

TextEng: Well, I should hope that they finally noticed a true hero.
Text: 음, 마침내 진정한 영웅을 알아본 것 같네.

TextEng: There is nothing to sing about. I just did my duty.
Text: 노래할 것 없어. 그냥 임무를 수행했을 뿐이야.

TextEng: Goodbye.
You work for Aarin Gend? Me work for Aarin too!
Text: 너 아린 겐드를 위해 일해? 나도 아린 위해 일해!

TextEng: So you're working for Aarin Gend?
Text: 그럼 아린 겐드를 위해 일하고 있는 거야?

TextEng: Why you stand here? You should look for Words.
Text: 왜 여기 서 있어? 너 권능의 언령 찾아야 해.

TextEng: You heard any rumors about where Words be? Me want to find them.
Text: 권능의 언령이 어디 있는지 소문 들었어? 나 그거 찾고 싶어.

TextEng: Why are you standing around here? Shouldn't you be looking for these Words?
Text: 왜 여기 서성이고 있어? 권능의 언령을 찾아야 하는 거 아니야?

TextEng: Me not need you.
Me get hurt lots. Me could use you in me search for Power Words.
Text: 나 많이 다쳐. 나 권능의 언령 찾는 거에서 너 필요해.

TextEng: Sorry, I'm not interested.
I could use a skilled healer in this dangerous search for the Words.
Text: 이 위험한 언령 탐색에 숙련된 치유사가 필요해.

TextEng: Have you heard any rumors as to where the Words could be?
Text: 권능의 언령이 어디 있을지에 대한 소문 들었어?

TextEng: What about them?
Me get really tired of you cheery, happy face.
Text: 나 너의 쾌활하고 행복한 얼굴 정말 지겨워.

TextEng: Me glad for see you again, Linu.
I'm getting tired of your silly, smiling face showing up wherever I go.
Text: 내가 가는 곳마다 나타나는 네 우스꽝스러운 웃는 얼굴이 지겨워지고 있어.

TextEng: It is good to see you again, Linu La'neral.
Me not need no help right now.
I don't need any help right now.
Me want you near me 'gain, Linu.
Text: 나 너 다시 나 가까이 있길 원해, 리누.

TextEng: I would love to have you travel with me again, Linu.
Text: 다시 너와 함께 여행하고 싶어, 리누.

TextEng: You know stuff 'bout Words of Power, Linu?
Text: 너 권능의 언령에 대해 아는 것 있어, 리누?

TextEng: Do you know anything about the Words of Power, Linu?
Text: 권능의 언령에 대해 아는 게 있어, 리누?

TextEng: What about them?
You silly, Linu. What happen to other ride?
Text: 웃기네, 리누. 다른 탈것은 어떻게 된 거야?

TextEng: Oh, Linu. What happened to the first ride?
Text: 아, 리누. 첫 번째 탈것은 어떻게 됐어?

TextEng: What you do to it?
What did you do to it?
Broke? How it broke?
Broke? How did it break?
Me always get good laugh 'round you, Linu.
Text: 나 항상 너 주변에서 재밌어, 리누.

TextEng: You never fail to surprise me, Linu.
Text: 넌 언제나 날 놀라게 하는구나, 리누.

TextEng: Did them drivers kick you out?
Did the wagoneers throw you out?
There be song 'bout me? I be real hero now!
Text: 나에 대한 노래가 있어? 나 이제 진짜 영웅이야!

TextEng: Bard sing about me? But me not do that much. Others help too.
Text: 음유시인이 나에 대해 노래해? 하지만 나 그렇게 많이 한 거 아니야. 다른 사람들도 도왔어.

TextEng: Bards are singing about me? Excellent.
Text: 음유시인들이 나에 대해 노래하고 있다고? 훌륭한데.

TextEng: Goodbye.
Change you clothes? What happen?
Changing your clothes?
You get mad at her?
Did you get mad at her?
She soak you clothes?
She soaked your clothes?
Me see where this going.
I think I'm getting the picture.
That mess you up?
So that messed you up?
You got bad luck!
Disaster follows you, doesn't it?
You wreck clothes in brawl?
And you wrecked your outfit in the brawl?
You tell me you get dirty that way, please.
Please tell me that's how you got dirty.
You get dirty cleaning up.
So you got dirty cleaning up?
Me not feel safe 'round you. Me go away now.
Text: 나 너 주변에서 안전하지 않아. 나 이제 가.

TextEng: I think I'll go somewhere else now. Maybe to a nice safe dragon lair.
Text: 다른 곳으로 가는 게 좋겠어. 안전한 용의 둥지 같은 곳으로.

TextEng: Why you not say that first time me ask?
Text: 왜 내가 처음 물었을 때 그렇게 말하지 않았어?

TextEng: Why didn't you just tell me you slipped in a puddle from the start?
You work for Aribeth? Me work for Aribeth too!
Text: 너 아리베스를 위해 일해? 나도 아리베스 위해 일해!

TextEng: Of course it be me. What you do to be hired to help?
Text: 당연히 나야. 너는 고용되려고 뭘 했어?

TextEng: So you're working for Aribeth?
Text: 그럼 아리베스를 위해 일하고 있는 거야?

TextEng: If you want catch cult, why you stand around here?
Text: 사교을 잡고 싶으면 왜 여기 서 있어?

TextEng: If you want to bring them to justice, why are you waiting in here?
Text: 그들을 정의의 심판에 넘기고 싶다면 왜 여기서 기다리고 있어?

TextEng: Sorry, me not interested.
Me need one who heal me wounds. You come.
Text: 나 내 상처 치유할 사람 필요해. 너 와.

TextEng: Sorry, but I'm not interested. Goodbye.
I often am in need of a skilled healer. Join me.
You hear any stuff about cult? Me looking for clues.
Text: 사교에 대해 뭐 들은 거 있어? 나 단서 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Have you heard any rumors about the cult since you've come here?
Text: 여기 온 이후로 사교에 대한 소문 들은 거 있어?

TextEng: Neverwinter Wood?
Why you be in here? You supposed to be finding cult.
Text: 왜 여기 있어? 너 사교 찾아야 하는 거 아니야.

TextEng: You gonna go find more about the woods?
Text: 숲에 대해 더 알아보러 갈 거야?

TextEng: Why are you waiting around in here? Should you be investigating the problem?
Text: 왜 여기서 기다리고 있어? 문제를 조사해야 하는 거 아니야?

TextEng: Are you planning to travel there?
A bard? But I didn't do that much. Everyone working for Aribeth helped.
Text: 음유시인? 하지만 나 그렇게 많이 한 거 아니야. 아리베스를 위해 일하는 모두가 도왔어.

TextEng: We say goodbye. Why you follow me here?
Me surprised me see you here, Linu.
I thought we parted ways. Why have you followed me?
Linu, what a pleasant surprise.
Me want you join me 'gain.
I want you to join me again.
Who you be 'gain?
Me want to ask questions.
Who are you again?
I want to ask you some questions.
Me not wanna talk to you. Goodbye.
Text: 나 너랑 얘기하고 싶지 않아. 안녕.

TextEng: I'm not in the mood to chat right now. Goodbye.
Who you be?
Who are you?
Go ahead.
No, me not. Why you ask?
No, I'm not. Why do you ask?
You seem to got problem with thief.
Text: 너 도적한테 문제 있는 것 같아.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> No-oooo. Me no be thief, honest.
That be all me, uh huh.
Me not like way you describe it, but yes, me a thief.
Text: 네가 말하는 방식은 싫지만, 그래, 나 도적이야.

TextEng: Sounds like you have something against thieves.
Text: 도적들에게 뭔가 불만이 있는 것 같네.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Lie]</Start> Uh, no.
That would pretty much sum me up, yes.
Text: 그게 나를 거의 요약하는 거지, 그래.

TextEng: I don't like the rest of the description, but I am a thief, yes.
Text: 나머지 설명은 싫지만, 나는 도적이야, 그래.

TextEng: She not need them now!
It's not like she needed them anymore!
What kind of thief you run into?
If it look like worth gold, maybe.
My gods woman! What kind of thieves have you run into?
Well, if it looked like it was actually worth something, maybe.
Text: 음, 실제로 가치 있어 보이면, 아마도.

TextEng: No.
No, me want know what happen.
Text: 아니, 나 무슨 일 있었는지 알고 싶어.

TextEng: No, tell me what happened.
Okay.
Why you be in barracks, not with sick people?
Text: 왜 병든 사람들이 아니라 병영에 있어?

TextEng: Why are you here in the barracks, rather than helping the plague victims?
Text: 역병 피해자들을 돕는 대신 여기 병영에 왜 있어?

TextEng: What happen next?
Then what happened?
Me not need you trippin' me all the time.
Text: 나 네가 계속 걸려 넘어지는 거 필요 없어.

TextEng: Just what I need, a cleric that's tripping and knocking things over every few minutes.
Text: 정말 필요한 게, 몇 분마다 걸려 넘어지고 물건을 쓰러뜨리는 성직자네.

TextEng: You really be so clumsy?
Are you really that clumsy?
That enough. Me not need more danger in life from you. Bye bye.
Text: 충분해. 나 너 때문에 더 위험한 거 필요 없어. 안녕.

TextEng: I've heard enough. You're dangerous to be around. Goodbye and better luck to you.
Text: 충분히 들었어. 네 주변은 위험해. 안녕, 행운을 빌어.

TextEng: Why you be here then?
Then why are you here?
That be good of you.
That's good of you.
That sound like thing that happen to you often.
Sounds typical for your luck.
Them attack person who helps sick people?
Text: 그들이 병든 사람 돕는 사람을 공격했어?

TextEng: They attacked you while you were helping plague victims?
Text: 역병 피해자들을 돕고 있을 때 공격했다고?

TextEng: Me looking for healer to help on mission.
Text: 나 임무 도와줄 치유사 찾고 있어.

TextEng: I'm looking for a good healer to help me in my mission.
Text: 임무를 도와줄 좋은 치유사를 찾고 있어.

TextEng: Me working for lady Aribeth. Can't tell you me mission. It secret.
Text: 나 아리베스 부인 위해 일해. 임무 말 못 해. 비밀이야.

TextEng: Me work for lady Aribeth. Me looking for creatures. They are important. They cure plague.
Text: 나 아리베스 부인 위해 일해. 나 생명체들 찾고 있어. 중요해. 역병 치료해.

TextEng: I work for Lady Aribeth. My mission is confidential.
Text: 아리베스 경을 위해 일하고 있어. 내 임무는 기밀이야.

TextEng: I work for Lady Aribeth. I must find several missing creatures that might be used to find a plague cure.
Text: 아리베스 경을 위해 일하고 있어. 역병 치료제를 찾는 데 사용될 수 있는 여러 실종된 생명체를 찾아야 해.

TextEng: What other stuff you know 'bout Blacklake district?
Text: 검은호수 구역에 대해 다른 거 알아?

TextEng: Do you know anything else about the Blacklake district?
Text: 검은호수 구역에 대해 다른 걸 아는 게 있어?

TextEng: Me go now.
Me looking for help in me mission.
Text: 나 내 임무 도와줄 사람 찾고 있어.

TextEng: No thanks. Goodbye.
What I need is someone to assist me on a mission.
Text: 내가 필요한 건 임무를 도와줄 사람이야.

TextEng: Bad stuff happens.
Well, that could happen to anyone.
Text: 음, 그건 누구에게나 일어날 수 있는 일이야.

TextEng: Who be Sehameme Moonbutt?
I don't think I've ever heard of Sehanine Moonbow.
Text: 세하닌 문보우에 대해 들어본 적이 없는 것 같아.

TextEng: Nevermind.
Me want you to level up. You be better with training.
Text: 나 네가 레벨업하길 원해. 훈련하면 나아질 거야.

TextEng: I'd like you to level up. You'd be more useful to me with a little training.
Text: 레벨업했으면 좋겠어. 약간의 훈련으로 더 유용해질 거야.

TextEng: Me no want you here no more.
Text: 나 이제 너 여기 원하지 않아.

TextEng: I think I'll do better off on my own.
Text: 혼자 하는 게 더 나을 것 같아.

TextEng: No. Stay.
Yes. Go.
We need change way you do stuff.
Text: 우리 네가 하는 방식 바꿔야 해.

TextEng: Me not want change anything else now.
Text: 나 지금 다른 거 바꾸고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: If me fail on locked door or chest you not help me.
Text: 내가 잠긴 문이나 상자 실패하면 너 나 돕지 마.

TextEng: If me fail on locked door or chest you help me.
Text: 내가 잠긴 문이나 상자 실패하면 너 나 도와.

TextEng: You start sneak quiet now.
You stop sneaking so quiet now.
Text: 너 이제 그렇게 조용히 잠행하는 거 그만해.

TextEng: You search all time when we move.
Text: 우리 움직일 때 너 항상 탐색해.

TextEng: You not search all time no more.
Text: 너 더 이상 항상 탐색하지 마.

TextEng: You need change how you heal me.
Text: 네가 날 치유하는 방법 바꿔야 해.

TextEng: You change how far away you stay.
Text: 네가 얼마나 멀리 떨어져 있는지 바꿔.

TextEng: I think we need to change your tactics.
I don't want to change anything else right now.
Text: 지금은 다른 걸 바꾸고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: If I fail to open a locked door or chest do not assist me.
Text: 잠긴 문이나 상자를 여는 데 실패하면 날 돕지 마.

TextEng: If I fail to open a locked door or chest please come to my aid.
Text: 잠긴 문이나 상자를 여는 데 실패하면 도와줘.

TextEng: Could you stop being so stealthy all the time?
Text: 항상 그렇게 은밀하게 다니는 거 그만둘 수 있어?

TextEng: Could you use more stealth when we travel?
Text: 우리가 여행할 때 더 은밀하게 다닐 수 있어?

TextEng: Could you please search when we move around?
Text: 우리가 돌아다닐 때 탐색해줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Could you not search all the time?
Could we change how quickly you decide to heal me?
Text: 날 치유하기로 결정하는 속도를 바꿀 수 있을까?

TextEng: You heal if me hurt real bad (below 25% of total hit points).
Text: 내가 정말 심하게 다치면 너 치유해 (전체 생명력의 25% 미만).

TextEng: You heal if me wounded (below 50% of total hit points).
Text: 내가 부상당하면 너 치유해 (전체 생명력의 50% 미만).

TextEng: You heal if me sort of hurt (below 75% of total hit points).
Text: 내가 좀 다치면 너 치유해 (전체 생명력의 75% 미만).

TextEng: Heal me if I become seriously wounded (below 25% of total hit points).
Heal me if I become wounded (below 50% of total hit points).
Heal me if I become somewhat injured (below 75% of total hit points).
We need to change the distance you stay away from me.
Text: 나로부터 떨어져 있는 거리를 바꿔야 해.

TextEng: Far distance.
Medium distance.
Stay close.
Me just wanna talk.
I just want to talk for a while.
Nevermind.
You got any hint or tip you give me 'bout this mission?
Text: 이 임무에 대해 내게 줄 힌트나 조언 있어?

TextEng: What you read?
What have you read?
Magic?
A ranger?
Me not want talk no more.
Text: 나 더 이상 얘기하고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: You know other stuff 'bout cult?
Text: 그 사교에 대해 다른 거 알아?

TextEng: That's enough information for now.
Is there anything else you know about the cult?
Text: 그 사교에 대해 아는 다른 게 있어?

TextEng: Tell me 'bout Blacklake district.
Tell me about the Blacklake district.
Me not want talk no more.
Text: 나 더 이상 얘기하고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: I think that's enough talking for now.
Anything else?
Do you have any advice or suggestions you can give me about my mission?
Text: 내 임무에 대해 줄 수 있는 조언이나 제안이 있어?

TextEng: Me want you to continue you story from before.
Text: 나 네가 전에 하던 이야기 계속하길 원해.

TextEng: I want you to continue your story from before.
You no let stupid seed get in way of me important quest!
Text: 바보 같은 씨앗이 내 중요한 퀘스트 방해하게 하지 마!

TextEng: You no worry 'bout seed. We find and make goddess happy.
Text: 씨앗 걱정하지 마. 우리 찾아서 여신 행복하게 할 거야.

TextEng: Me found strange seed! This be you seed?
Text: 나 이상한 씨앗 찾았어! 이게 네 씨앗이야?

TextEng: No stupid seed had better get in the way of our important quest.
Text: 바보 같은 씨앗이 우리의 중요한 퀘스트를 방해하는 게 낫겠어.

TextEng: Don't worry Linu, we will find the seed, somehow.
Text: 걱정 마 리누, 어떻게든 씨앗을 찾을 거야.

TextEng: I have an unusual seed right here. Is this it?
That be it? Not get anything new?
Me thank you for making it be stronger, Linu.
That's it? Nothing new?
Thank you for unlocking its full power, Linu.
What you do with seed now, Linu?
Text: 이제 씨앗 가지고 뭐 할 거야, 리누?

TextEng: What will you do with the seed now, Linu?
Text: 이제 씨앗으로 뭘 할 거야, 리누?

TextEng: And what 'bout you?
What about you?
I care for you as friend, more than any magic item.
Text: 나 너를 친구로 생각해, 어떤 마법 아이템보다도.

TextEng: Your friendship means more to me than any magical item.
Text: 네 우정이 어떤 마법 아이템보다도 소중해.

TextEng: No, and I really don't care. I think you're moving a little fast for me.
Text: 아니, 그리고 정말 관심 없어. 너무 빨리 가는 것 같은데.

TextEng: No, please tell me.
Yes, but I don't feel that way about you.
Text: 그래, 하지만 나는 너한테 그런 감정 없어.

TextEng: Yes. You complete me too, dear Linu.
Text: 그래. 나도 네가 날 완전하게 만들어, 사랑하는 리누.

TextEng: I would like that very much.
Me change mind. Me no want hear you story.
Text: 마음 바뀌었어. 나 너의 이야기 듣고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: I've changed my mind. I don't really want to hear this.
Text: 마음이 바뀌었어. 이거 정말 듣고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: Tell me what they say.
Tell me what they said.
How long she look at tree for?
How long did she stand there looking at the trees?
What happen?
What happened?
You still be dreaming, maybe?
Are you sure you weren't still dreaming?
Floating?
<StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Beauty standing amidst fiery destruction. That's you!
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 불타는 파괴 속에 서 있는 아름다움. 그게 너야!

TextEng: That amazing.
That's amazing.
People die all time, why goddess cry over stupid tree.
Text: 사람들은 항상 죽는데, 왜 여신이 바보 같은 나무 때문에 울어.

TextEng: People die every day, but this goddess cries over a tree?
Text: 사람들은 매일 죽는데, 이 여신은 나무 때문에 우는 거야?

TextEng: Where them go?
What happened to them?
Me could stare at you like that.
Text: 나도 너를 그렇게 바라볼 수 있어.

TextEng: The way I could stand and admire your beauty for endless hours.
Text: 끝없이 서서 네 아름다움을 감상할 수 있을 것 같아.

TextEng: Me want hear it.
I want to hear it.
You get bored with magic stuff?
Text: 마법 물건 가지고 노는 게 지겨웠어?

TextEng: You were bored playing with magic items?
Text: 마법 아이템 가지고 노는 게 지겨웠어?

TextEng: Go on.
Me think anyone else die if them was you.
Text: 나 생각엔 다른 사람이었으면 죽었을 거야.

TextEng: I don't think anybody else could survive what you have.
Text: 네가 겪은 걸 다른 누구도 살아남지 못했을 거야.

TextEng: Cursed.
Both, me think.
Both, I think.
It be blessing. Me like danger and beauty in woman.
Text: 축복이야. 나 여자의 위험과 아름다움 좋아해.

TextEng: I think it's a blessing. You are the most dangerous, yet exciting woman I have ever met.
Text: 축복이라고 생각해. 넌 내가 만난 가장 위험하면서도 흥미진진한 여자야.

TextEng: Hey, me not look for true love, me just say nice words to friend.
Text: 이봐, 나 진정한 사랑 찾는 거 아니야, 그냥 친구한테 좋은 말 한 거야.

TextEng: Woah! Deeper relationship? It was just a compliment.
Text: 워! 더 깊은 관계? 그냥 칭찬이었어.

TextEng: Then me not want to hear you story no more.
Text: 그럼 나 너의 이야기 더 이상 듣고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: Then I don't want to listen to your whiny stories anymore.
Text: 그럼 너의 징징대는 이야기 더 이상 듣고 싶지 않아.

TextEng: Me not care what you think of me. We go now.
Text: 나 네가 나에 대해 어떻게 생각하는지 신경 안 써. 이제 가자.

TextEng: I really don't care what you think. Let's get going.
Text: 네가 어떻게 생각하는지 정말 신경 안 써. 가자.

TextEng: Me just make joke. You tell me you story, please.
Text: 나 그냥 농담한 거야. 너의 이야기 말해줘.

TextEng: I was just joking, Linu. Calm yourself and continue your story.
You go on with you story then.
Then let's continue your story.
So how you live?
So how did you survive?
What you do?
What did you see?
Who it be?
Who was it?
What voice say to you?
What did the voice say?
What she say?
What did she say?
How she make him stop?
How did she stop him?
Me knew that already.
I already figured that out.
No! You saved by goddess.
Wait, you were rescued by a goddess?
You need be glad she save you life!
Text: 그녀가 네 목숨 구해준 거 기뻐해야 해!

TextEng: How could you be ungrateful for such a gift?
Text: 어떻게 그런 선물에 감사하지 않을 수 있어?

TextEng: A task?
That seem more than lucky to me.
Text: 그건 나한테 운 이상인 것 같아.

TextEng: That does seem to stretch the limits of luck.
Text: 그건 운의 한계를 넘는 것 같은데.

TextEng: You no blow place up, did you?
You didn't destroy the place, did you?
That's trouble.
What make you decide to become cleric?
What made you decide that you should be a cleric?
Text: 무엇이 성직자가 되어야 한다고 결정하게 했어?

TextEng: But you no be like them?
But you didn't take after them?
What be this 'potentials'?
What are 'potentials'?
Them were very wrong.
Boy, were they wrong.
Okay, tell more.
Okay, go on.
You be worse then than now.
I didn't think it was possible for you to be worse than you are now.
Text: 지금보다 더 심할 수 있다고는 생각 못 했어.

TextEng: What you mean you move in?
What do you mean by moved in?
Me kick you out too, if you do such stupid thing.
Text: 나도 그런 바보 같은 짓 하면 너 내쫓을 거야.

TextEng: I'd have kicked you out too, how stupid.
Text: 나도 널 내쫓았을 거야, 얼마나 멍청해.

TextEng: So he kick you out?
So he kicked you out?
Little trip?
What fate you talking 'bout?
What fate would that be?
Me want you keep talking 'bout story you start before.
Text: 나 너 전에 시작한 이야기 계속하길 원해.

TextEng: I'd like you to tell me more of your story, Linu.
Text: 네 이야기를 더 들려줬으면 해, 리누.

TextEng: You no let thinking of husband get in way you job!
Text: 너 남편 생각이 너 일 방해하게 하지 마!

TextEng: No worry, we find book and then we know what happen to you husband.
Text: 걱정 마, 우리 책 찾아서 너 남편한테 무슨 일 있었는지 알 거야.

TextEng: Me find book with you husband's name on it.
Text: 나 너 남편 이름 있는 책 찾았어.

TextEng: Just don't let this get in the way of your other duties.
Don't worry, we'll find the journal and discover what happened to your husband.
Text: 걱정 마, 일지를 찾아서 네 남편에게 무슨 일이 있었는지 알아낼 거야.

TextEng: I found this journal. It has your husband's name on it.
Text: 이 일지를 찾았어. 네 남편 이름이 있어.

TextEng: Quit whining! Him dead long ago; you be over him.
Text: 징징대지 마! 그 오래전에 죽었어; 너 이제 넘어가.

TextEng: Quit whining Linu. He's been dead for a long time, get over it.
Text: 징징대지 마 리누. 죽은 지 오래됐어, 이제 넘어가.

TextEng: You no stop now. You promise you help me, now you do!
Text: 너 지금 그만두지 마. 너 나 돕겠다고 약속했어, 이제 해!

TextEng: Don't you back out on me now. You made a commitment and you had better fulfill it!
Text: 지금 빠져나가려 하지 마. 약속했으니 지켜야 해!

TextEng: Me no leave you, Linu. You be strong and make Synth proud.
Text: 나 너 떠나지 않아, 리누. 너 강해지고 신스 자랑스럽게 만들어.

TextEng: I won't leave you, Linu. You must be strong and go on, as Synth wanted you to.
Text: 널 떠나지 않을게, 리누. 신스가 원했던 대로 강해지고 계속 나아가야 해.

TextEng: It no you fault, Linu. Me no leave you.
Text: 그거 너 잘못 아니야, 리누. 나 너 떠나지 않아.

TextEng: It wasn't your fault, Linu. I'm not going to leave you.
Text: 네 잘못이 아니야, 리누. 널 떠나지 않을 거야.

TextEng: That be it?
That be good reward. Me like pretty pendant.
Text: 그거 좋은 보상이야. 나 예쁜 펜던트 좋아해.

TextEng: That's it, huh?
That is a wonderful gift, Linu, thank you.
Temple no could party without you?
Text: 신전 너 없이 파티 못 했어?

TextEng: So? Why couldn't they do it without you?
Text: 그래서? 왜 너 없이 못 한 거야?

TextEng: Him no wait for you?
He wouldn't wait for you?
He keeping stuff like affair from you?
Text: 그 불륜 같은 거 너한테 숨기고 있었어?

TextEng: You figure he was fooling around on you?
Why you wish that?
Why is that?
Ten stories? You parents be rich?
Ten story wall? Your parent's must be rich.
What happen?
What happened?
Me be sure never to wake you at night.
Text: 나 밤에 절대 너 깨우지 않을게.

TextEng: Remind me never to try to wake you quietly in the night.
Text: 밤에 조용히 깨우려 하지 말라고 일깨워줘.

TextEng: You break his jaw?
You mean you broke his jaw?
You just one bad thing after 'nother.
Text: 너 그냥 나쁜 일 하나에서 또 다른 거.

TextEng: You're just one calamity after another, aren't you?
You didn't.
Tell me you didn't.
He live, I guess.
At least he survived.
That not burst his head open or stuff?
Text: 그거 그의 머리 터뜨리거나 그런 거 아니었어?

TextEng: And that didn't kill him or turn him into a frog or something?
Text: 그래서 죽거나 개구리로 변하거나 한 건 아니었어?

TextEng: Him forgive you?
Did he forgive you?
What you mean by that?
You mean you... ?
Good move!
Ha, you bad luck kill him?
Text: 하, 너 운 나빠서 그 죽었어?

TextEng: What? Did you kill him finally?
Why they not last? What happen?
Text: 왜 그들 안 지속됐어? 무슨 일 있었어?

TextEng: What do you mean? What happened?
Good for you!
How you like being adventurer?
Tell me, how do you like being an adventurer?
Who that be?
Oh? Who is that?
YOU catch him for husband?
And YOU managed to hook him?
You husband.
Your husband.
You think you be pretty smart, huh?
Thought you were pretty smart, huh?
It be that bad?
Was it really that bad?
What he do?
What did he do?
Me want you continue you story from before.
Text: 나 너 전에 하던 이야기 계속하길 원해.

TextEng: Tell me more about your story.
You not let you search get in way of stuff you do for me!
Text: 너 너 찾는 거 나 위해 하는 일 방해하게 하지 마!

TextEng: If me find it me let you know.
Text: 나 그거 찾으면 나 너한테 알려줘.

TextEng: Me found cup! This be cup you talk 'bout?
Text: 나 잔 찾았어! 이거 너 말하던 잔이야?

TextEng: Just don't let your quest get in the way of mine. You work for me, not the other way around.
Text: 네 퀘스트가 내 것을 방해하지 않게 해. 넌 나를 위해 일하는 거지, 반대가 아니야.

TextEng: If I find it I'll let you know.
Is this the chalice you were talking about?
That's it? A pendant?
Thank you, Linu.
Why me ever pick you as friend, me just not know.
Text: 왜 나 너를 친구로 골랐는지, 나 그냥 몰라.

TextEng: Why did I ever decide to pick you as a companion?
How you lose it?
How did you lose it?
How it possible you lose chalice again?
Text: 어떻게 가능해 너 성배 또 잃어버렸어?

TextEng: How in the name of all that is holy did you lose it again?
He have bad luck like you.
Sounds like he had just about as much luck as you do.
How you know this stuff?
How did you find all of this out?
That take real gall!
That just like a Zhent.
Me can't believe he did that!
Text: 나 그가 그랬다는 거 믿을 수 없어!

TextEng: Now that takes a lot of gall.
That's a Zhent for you.
I can't believe he would do that!
Old woman beat you up?
That terrible.
You got beat up by an old woman?
That's horrible.
Forget cup then. He probably sell it and you never find it 'gain.
Text: 잔 잊어버려. 그 아마 팔았어 그리고 너 다시는 못 찾을 거야.

TextEng: You no worry Linu, me help you find cup.
Text: 너 걱정 마 리누, 나 너 잔 찾는 거 도와줄게.

TextEng: Better forget about it then. He probably sold it and you'll never find it again.
Text: 그럼 잊어버리는 게 나아. 아마 팔았을 거고 다시 못 찾을 거야.

TextEng: Don't worry Linu, I'll help you find the chalice.
Text: 걱정 마 리누, 성작 찾는 거 도와줄게.

TextEng: What about other priests?
You lost a gift from a goddess?
She show you city destroyed if you stay?
Text: 너 머물면 도시 파괴되는 거 보여줬어?

TextEng: What you see in vision?
What, did she tell you to get the hell out of Evereska before you doomed them all?
Text: 뭐, 모두를 파멸시키기 전에 에버레스카에서 꺼지라고 했어?

TextEng: What happened in the vision?
Me not used to calling other people slow, but...
Text: 나 다른 사람들 느리다고 부르는 거 익숙하지 않은데...

TextEng: It be good that they be very happy for you.
Text: 그들이 너 위해 정말 기뻐하는 거야.

TextEng: You're just a little clueless aren't you?
Yes, I'm sure they were very happy... for you.
Text: 그래, 정말 기뻤을 거야... 널 위해서 말이야.

TextEng: Good. Me not paying you for you to quest! You here to keep me 'live and stuff!
Text: 좋아. 나 너한테 퀘스트하라고 돈 주는 거 아니야! 너 나 살려두려고 여기 있는 거야!

TextEng: Good. I'm paying you to keep me alive, not to worry about some stupid quest.
Text: 좋아. 나 바보 같은 퀘스트 걱정하라고 돈 주는 게 아니라 날 살려두라고 주는 거야.

TextEng: Me help you find it, Linu. We be good team.
Text: 나 너 찾는 거 도와줄게, 리누. 우리 좋은 팀이야.

TextEng: We can find it, Linu, if we work together.
Text: 찾을 수 있어, 리누, 우리가 함께 일하면.

TextEng: Me want help you, Linu.
Surely it has not failed. You will find it someday.
Text: 분명 실패한 게 아니야. 언젠가 찾을 거야.

TextEng: That be what thief took.
And that is what was stolen?
Me wanna know 'bout you, if we be working together.
Text: 나 너에 대해 알고 싶어, 우리 함께 일하면.

TextEng: If we're going to be working together, I'd like to know more about you.
Text: 함께 일할 거라면, 너에 대해 더 알고 싶어.

TextEng: What you remember 'bout you home?
What you problem with thieves be?
Why you leave you home?
What are your memories of your home like?
Them make fun of humans?
Me would have beat them up for being mean.
(Snicker) That be funny... I mean bad.
You have good times too, yes?
Do elven children really call each other humans, in a bad way?
Text: 엘프 아이들이 정말 서로 인간이라고 나쁘게 불러?

TextEng: I'd have beat some sense into them.
(Snicker) That's, um... terrible Linu.
There were good times too, right?
What happened to make you hate thieves so much?
Text: 무슨 일이 있었길래 도적들을 그렇게 싫어해?

TextEng: Why did you leave your homeland?
You no bring bad luck to me! Me got 'nuff problems.
Text: 너 나한테 불운 가져오지 마! 나 문제 충분히 있어.

TextEng: When me born, me mom dropped me on head. I got some bad luck too.
Text: 나 태어날 때, 나의 엄마가 나 머리로 떨어뜨렸어. 나도 불운 좀 있어.

TextEng: You'd better not bring any bad luck my way.
Text: 내 쪽으로 불운 가져오지 않는 게 좋을 거야.

TextEng: Well, bad luck happens to all of us at one time or other.
You be walking trouble. You no bring you troubles to me.
Text: 너 걸어다니는 문제야. 너 너의 문제 나한테 가져오지 마.

TextEng: You really are a piece of work. You better not bring catastrophe down on me.
Text: 너 정말 골칫거리야. 나한테 재앙 가져오지 않는 게 좋을 거야.

TextEng: What did thief take?
What did the thief steal?
Fine. You no let you problems get in me way.
Text: 좋아. 너 너의 문제가 나의 길 막게 하지 마.

TextEng: It okay, Linu. Me want know what you talking about.
Text: 괜찮아, 리누. 나 너 무슨 얘기하는지 알고 싶어.

TextEng: Fine, just don't let your problems get in my way.
Text: 좋아, 네 문제가 내 길을 막지만 않으면 돼.

TextEng: No, Linu. I want to hear what you had to say.
Text: 아니, 리누. 네가 하려던 말 듣고 싶어.

TextEng: You not use ranged weapons no more. Use melee weapons when you fight.
Text: 너 더 이상 원거리 무기 쓰지 마. 싸울 때 근접 무기 써.

TextEng: You not use melee weapon no more. Use ranged weapons and stuff.
Text: 너 더 이상 근접 무기 쓰지 마. 원거리 무기 같은 거 써.

TextEng: Don't use your ranged weapons anymore. Use your melee weapons in combat.
Text: 이제 원거리 무기 쓰지 마. 전투에서 근접 무기 써.

TextEng: Don't use your melee weapons anymore. Use your ranged weapons in combat.
Text: 이제 근접 무기 쓰지 마. 전투에서 원거리 무기 써.

TextEng: Me too busy, you quiet now, Linu.
Text: 나 너무 바빠, 너 이제 조용히 해, 리누.

TextEng: I'm too busy right now, Linu.
Me gots no time for you whining. We go now.
Text: 나 너 징징거리는 거 들을 시간 없어. 우리 이제 가.

TextEng: I have no time for your chatter. Let's go.
Text: 네 수다 들을 시간 없어. 가자.

TextEng: *Sigh* Okay. What you want say?
*Sigh* All right. What did you want to say?
What you want talk 'bout, Linu?
Yes Linu, what did you want to talk about?
Text: 그래 리누, 무엇에 대해 얘기하고 싶었어?

TextEng: Ya big deal. We go now, right?
What ever. Let's just get going, okay?
That be part of hero job. Me must make others be strong too.
Text: 그게 영웅 일의 일부야. 나 다른 사람들도 강하게 만들어야 해.

TextEng: That's the job of a hero. We inspire others to greatness.
Text: 그게 영웅의 일이야. 우리는 다른 이들에게 위대함을 고취시켜.

TextEng: You be hero like me, Linu. We be team.
Text: 너 나처럼 영웅이야, 리누. 우리 팀이야.

TextEng: We have been a team, Linu. You too are a hero.
Okay, Linu, me get point.
Okay Linu, I get the point.
'Nuff talk. We go fight now.
Text: 충분히 얘기했어. 우리 이제 싸우러 가.

TextEng: Enough speeches, we need to get going now.
Thank you, Linu.
Linu, me not see you do clumsy things whole time we be team. Maybe you just be nervous lots?
Text: 리누, 나 우리 팀 되고 내내 너 서투른 짓 하는 거 못 봤어. 아마 너 그냥 많이 긴장했던 거 아니야?

TextEng: Linu, in all the time we have been together, you have never done any of these clumsy things. Maybe it's just a lack of confidence.
Text: 리누, 우리가 함께한 모든 시간 동안, 너는 이런 서투른 짓을 한 적이 없었어. 아마 그냥 자신감 부족일 거야.
